<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA60">
<l>caraṇā maṟaipayanta tāmaraiyā ṉōṭu</l>
<l>maraṇāya maṉṉuyirkaṭ kellā – maraṇāya</l>
<l>pērāḻi koṇṭa pirāṉaṉṟi maṟṟaṟiyā</l>
<l>tōrāḻi cūḻnta vulaku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It does not know any other lord than the one who took the big discus</l>
<l>as protection for all living beings who are mortal</l>
<l>along with him from the lotus who yielded the Vedas as a refuge,</l>
<l>– [this] world surrounded by one ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
